Use the standard library
This is how to pairs_sum_to_zero of l:
   Remember that n is l's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that a is item i in l
      Remember that j is sum of i and 1
      Remember that rest is diff of n and j
      Do this rest times:
         Remember that b is item j in l
         When sum of a and b is 0, then:
            The answer is 1
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 0
Now you know
>>> pairs_sum_to_zero of [1, 3, 5, 0] 
0
>>> pairs_sum_to_zero of [1, 3, -2, 1] 
0
>>> pairs_sum_to_zero of [1, 2, 3, 7] 
0